    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.25.34-35_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">34</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">CORNELL UNIVERSITY
                        <lb/>
                    ITHACA, NEW YORK
                        <lb/>
                    DEPARTMENT OF ENGLISH</hi>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>December 2, 1957</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Thank you very much for your find letter of November 24. Also I enjoyed pictures of you in a magazine from the Univ. of Missouri which Slade Kendrick brought me: Your wife! but of you is magnificent. I believe it is the same one photographed for the dust-cover of your great epic.</p>
                
                <p>I have been rather feeble, spent most of the Thanksgiving holiday in bed, <del/><add>but</add> now feel no nausea &#8212; <unclear/> teach my seminar this
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.25.34-35_0002"/>
                    
                    afternoon.</p>
                
                <p>I certainly wish that I <hi rend="underline">were</hi> your neighbor, but even away out there you are an inspiration to me.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>God bless you,</salute>
                    <signed>Harold Thompson</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="curatorial"><hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT CENTER</hi></note>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.25.34-35_0003"/>
                
                <ab type="return">
                    <add><hi rend="caps">H.<unclear/>T.</hi></add>
                    Department of English
                        <lb/>
                    <hi rend="caps">CORNELL UNIVERSITY
                        <lb/>
                    ITHACA, N. Y.</hi>
                </ab>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">35</fw>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    ITHACA, DEC 2 6-PM 1957 N.Y.    
                </ab>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>3 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p>U.S. POSTAGE 3Â¢ IN GOD WE TRUST LIBERTY</p>
